## Service detail, How It Works delivery lifecycles
Keep `delivery_process` aligned across `getDeliverySteps()` (`ServiceDetailDeliverySection.tsx`), `scripts/lib/pdpCopyGenerator.ts`, and Supabase `product_content` seed/migrations:
- **Assess (advisory)**: Scope (Days 1-2) ‚Üí Assess (Days 3-4) ‚Üí Advise (Day 5); total `1 Week`
- **Design / AI Design**: Discover ‚Üí Design ‚Üí Handover (seed); code fallback may use 4 steps
- **Deploy / AI Deploy**: Prepare ‚Üí Build ‚Üí Go live
- **Managed**: Onboard (Week 1) ‚Üí Operate (Ongoing) ‚Üí Improve (Ongoing); total `Ongoing`
- Do not ship single-step Assess or Managed lifecycles in PDP seed data; PDP content overrides code fallbacks when Supabase catalog is enabled

